items.text: This dashboard presents Branch and Group-level data as informed by your level of access. Please note that all members and managers of a Branch may not also be members or managers of a Group, and that a user could be a member or manager of multiple Groups, so the top row values are not always equal to the sum of the values in each Group-level row represented in the table at bottom.

widgets.title: How is each group progressing and performing?
